document_data.name: Fael Olyphar
document_data.mainbody: '''Fael Olyphar''' was one of the common [[drow]] families of [[Menzoberranzan]] in the [[Northdark]] in the late 14{{th}} and 15{{th}} centuries [[DR]].
document_data.History: The Fael Olyphar family was founded sometime before the [[Spellplague]] years of the late 14{{th}} and 15{{th}} centuries DR. Their estate stood in the [[Menzoberranzan/Eastmyr|Eastmyr]] neighborhood of Menzoberranzan, amongst other less successful drow families: [[Asbodela]], [[Dlaen Dei'Amatar]], [[Ilystryph]], [[Uluar]], and [[Zalyzryn]].
